00:39:55,640 --> 00:39:58,840
ظآزIn that sentimental and first timeظآز

399
00:39:58,872 --> 00:40:01,611
ظآزRecalling the youthظآز

400
00:40:15,147 --> 00:40:21,912
(Vanished Name)

401
00:40:26,804 --> 00:40:28,564
(Ren Xiaoming
influenced the police case.)

402
00:40:28,564 --> 00:40:31,494
(According to China's Public Security
Administration Punishments Law's)

403
00:40:31,494 --> 00:40:34,776
(article 60, she was detained
for five days with a 500-yuan fine.)

404
00:40:35,243 --> 00:40:37,833
(Bai Shu was sentenced to three years
due to illegal firearm possession.)

405
00:40:37,833 --> 00:40:40,413
(Her obstruction
of police investigations was a crime.)

406
00:40:40,413 --> 00:40:42,493
(Combined sentencing
resulted in a four-year prison term.)

407
00:40:42,493 --> 00:40:44,450
(Later, she got a reduced sentence
for good behavior in prison.)

408
00:40:45,656 --> 00:40:47,366
(Since the case in 2010, Ge Wenjun)

409
00:40:47,366 --> 00:40:49,606
(never surrendered to authorities
and evaded investigation long-term.)

410
00:40:49,606 --> 00:40:51,716
(The task force rebuilt the crime scene
evidence chain and identified her.)

411
00:40:51,716 --> 00:40:54,746
(Ge Wenjun was convicted of murder
and sentenced to death.)

412
00:40:54,746 --> 00:40:57,528
(Also convicted of witness tampering,
she was ultimately executed.)

413
00:40:58,614 --> 00:41:00,474
(Zhang Fang was sentenced to three years
for harboring criminals.)

414
00:41:00,474 --> 00:41:02,841
(Upon release, he returned to Qidaohezi
and resumed driving.)

415
00:41:03,479 --> 00:41:07,036
(Liu Xiaoran was convicted of assault
and sentenced to five years.)

416
00:41:07,419 --> 00:41:08,999
(Supported by the Women's Federation
and social welfare, Yamei went to school.)

417
00:41:08,999 --> 00:41:10,648
(The mute girl finally learned
to write her own name.)

418
00:41:11,256 --> 00:41:15,526
(Chen Junhang fully recovered
from the blunt head trauma.)

419
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:19,610
(Zhou Yun lent her ID card.
Wen Yuxiu misused another's ID.)

420
00:41:19,610 --> 00:41:23,640
(They violated relevant provisions
of China's Resident Identity Card Law.)

421
00:41:23,640 --> 00:41:28,728
(With no malicious intent,
the police chose not to press charges.)

422
00:41:30,268 --> 00:41:31,478
(He Yuqiong's mother, Li Ping,)

423
00:41:31,478 --> 00:41:33,958
(got better with the community's
and Xiaoming's care.)

424
00:41:33,958 --> 00:41:35,783
(People rescued by He Yuqiong
often visited her.)

425
00:41:36,650 --> 00:41:39,170
(Ren Xiaofei and Li Wancheng
continued living in the old place.)

426
00:41:39,170 --> 00:41:40,848
(They remained safe and happy.)

427
00:41:41,406 --> 00:41:43,016
(Wen Yuxiu lived quietly
and became the community librarian.)

428
00:41:43,016 --> 00:41:44,736
(She often read stories to children
and taught them about dreams.)

429
00:41:44,736 --> 00:41:45,636
(Just as she once
taught Xiaoming and Bai Shu.)

430
00:41:45,636 --> 00:41:46,832
(She often remembered
her dear friend, Ren Meiyan.)

431
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:54,904
(Bai Shu learned everything
her biological mother had done for her.)

432
00:41:55,064 --> 00:41:57,912
(She had always protected her.)

433
00:41:57,912 --> 00:42:03,928
(The unspoken 'Mom' became
her deepest, lifelong regret.)

434
00:42:03,928 --> 00:42:08,792
(Later, she erected a tombstone
for her mother at the cemetery.)

435
00:42:08,792 --> 00:42:14,712
(As her daughter, she finally completed
their long-delayed reunion.)

436
00:42:20,728 --> 00:42:25,678
(When investigating the 1.21 case,
Qidaohezi Criminal Investigation Unit)

437
00:42:25,678 --> 00:42:29,618
(overcame challenges like the case's age
and scarce physical evidence,)

438
00:42:29,618 --> 00:42:33,358
(maintained multi-unit coordination
and cross-departmental collaboration,)

439
00:42:33,358 --> 00:42:37,508
(utilized big data analysis, DNA,
fingerprint matching, and so on)

440
00:42:37,508 --> 00:42:42,338
(to meticulously screen vast data
to pinpoint crucial evidence,)

441
00:42:42,338 --> 00:42:48,098
(apprehend Ge Wenjun,
and rescue the imprisoned victim.)

442
00:42:48,098 --> 00:42:50,448
(To honor excellence and boost morale,)

443
00:42:50,448 --> 00:42:54,948
(per regulations
in the Police Awards Ordinance,)

444
00:42:54,948 --> 00:42:59,098
(the 1.21 task force earned
a first-class merit citation.)

445
00:42:59,098 --> 00:43:01,592
(Li Meng and others received
commendations for meritorious service.)

446
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
